This MATLAB experiment is built using two packages, PsychToolBox and DotsX.

PSYCHTOOLBOX:
Instructions for obtaining this program are online:
http://psychtoolbox.org/wikka.php?wakka=PsychtoolboxDownload
This project uses a combination of SVN and matlab scripts to stay up-to-date.

DOTSX:
This program is maintained online at:
http://code.google.com/p/dotsx/
The SVN can be accessed anonymously over http at the following address:
http://dotsx.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/DotsX